        <div class="container-1">
            <div class="col align-self-center">
            <h6 class="display-4">How do you feel today ?</h6></div>
        <br>
        <h4>Click on "very much" if you feel very strong towards that emotion.</h4>
        <h4>Click on "not much" if you feel exact opposite of that emotion.</h4>
        <h4>Click on "that's me" if your feeling aligns with that particular emotion. Please pick one. ❤️</h4>
